oofem.out
3D periodic lattice mass-transport on a small RVE with a sphere inclusion
nltransienttransportproblem nsteps 1 deltat 1.0 rtol 0.001 alpha 1. nsmax 200 contextOutputStep 100 nmodules 1
errorcheck
domain 3dMassLatticeTransport
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_all
ncrosssect 1 nmat 3 nbc 2 nic 0 nltf 1
simpletransportcs 1 mat 1
latticetransmat 1 d 1.e3 k 1.e-19 vis 1.e-3 thetas 1.
latticetransmat 2 d 1.e3 k 1.e-22 vis 1.e-3 thetas 1.
latticetransmat 3 d 1.e3 k 1.e-19 vis 1.e-3 thetas 1.
BoundaryCondition 1 loadTimeFunction 1 prescribedvalue 0.
BoundaryCondition 2 loadTimeFunction 1 prescribedvalue 1.
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.
#@grid 3dTM
#@mesher qhull
#@diam 0.0005
#@perflag 3 1 1 1
#@prism 1 box 6 0. 0. 0. 0.00625 0.00625 0.00625
#@sphereinclusion 1 centre 3 0.003125 0.003125 0.003125 radius 0.002 itz 1.e-5 inside 2 interface 3
